OL,3,CThe Welsh veteran who paved the way
OL,4,Cfor the allied advance after D-Day
OL,6,FThe work of the Royal Engineers proved
OL,7,Fdeadly for one of his comrades,
OL,8,FCorporal Wray.
OL,10,FRichard said, "We dug up this
OL,11,Fobstacle, when the bulldozer started
OL,12,Fpulling a Tellermine went off. Next
OL,13,Fthing I knew he was sprawling by the
OL,14,Fside of me and that was it."
OL,16,FWith the beachhead secure, the next
OL,17,Fstage was to install the Mulberry
OL,18,Fharbours.
